                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/beast/2_MIKHAIL5_070_006_1",
                    "text": "%BEAST%: Greetings, my friend. Why the big smile?",
                    "textb": "%BEAST%: I suppose I should thank you; even if you're only here because Charles sent you.",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                        "line": {
                            "text": "%PLAYER%: Destiny had predicted you were going to die. I'm glad she was wrong.",
                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: I also wanted to see if Destiny was right. She had predicted you were going to die.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/2_MIKHAIL5_070_003_3",
                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/beast/2_MIKHAIL5_070_006_3",
                                    "text": "%BEAST%: Well, for all intents and purposes, it appeared as though I was deceased. So her prediction did come true, in a sense.",
                                    "textb": "%BEAST%: How nice. You should be pleased to know the prediction was correct - in a sense anyway. It did appear as if I was no longer among the living.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "text": "%PLAYER%: Blink, we found Beast and he's safe. Could you open up a portal back to Avalon?",
                                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: Blink, you can tell Xavier his friend Beast is alive. And could you open portal back to Avalon?",
                                            "response": {
                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                "line": {
                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/blink/2_MIKHAIL5_070_003_5",
                                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/blink/2_MIKHAIL5_070_006_5",
                                                    "text": "%BLINK%: I'd love to. One minute and it'll be there. Professor Xavier's really happy to hear your friend Beast is okay. Stop by and see him the next time you're at Avalon.",
                                                    "textb": "%BLINK%: Sure, just wait a minute and the portal will be there. Professor Xavier's really relieved to hear Beast is fine. Be sure to talk to the Professor the next time you're in Avalon - he wants to congratulate you.",
                                                    "response": {
                                                        "chosenscriptfile": "act2/mikhail/openblinkportal",
                                                        "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                        "text": "%BLANK%"
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "startCondition": {
